===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /kwa/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /kwa/

'''quoi'''
===Homophones===
[[coi]]

===Pronoun===
# [[What]]
# {{frslang}} [[aught]], [[anything]], [[something]]
#:''Ya quoi à faire en Angleterre?''
#::''Is there aught to do in England?''

===Particle===
'''quoi'''
# (''colloquial'') [[you know]], [[like]], [[y'know]].
#:''Alors, ce mec m'a dit de lui donner mon porte-monnaie, quoi.''
#::''So, this guy told me to give me his wallet, like.''

